# BIZDRIVE video workflow — API keys
#
# Copy this file to .env IN THIS FOLDER and fill in keys:
#   cp templates/_shared/env/.env.example templates/_shared/env/.env
#
# .env is gitignored. NEVER commit real keys.
# tools/setup.sh creates .env from this file automatically.

# ============ REQUIRED ============

# ElevenLabs Scribe v2 — Thai speech-to-text (the pipeline's STT engine).
# Required for Step 2 + Step 9. ~$0.024 per 100-second clip.
# Get a key: https://elevenlabs.io/app/settings/api-keys
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=

# ============ OPTIONAL ============

# OpenRouter — AI B-roll video generation (Step 14).
# Default model bytedance/seedance-1-5-pro, ~$0.02 per 3-5s clip.
# Only needed if the job uses AI-generated B-roll.
# Get a key: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=

# Pexels — fresh stock B-roll download (alternative to AI generation).
# Get a key: https://www.pexels.com/api/
# PEXELS_API_KEY=

# OpenAI Whisper — English STT fallback (not used for Thai content).
# OPENAI_API_KEY=

# xAI Grok — fast/free English STT draft (phrase-level only).
# XAI_API_KEY=
